OL,7,FNew dashcam data obtained by ITV News
OL,8,Freveals the sheer scale of dangerous
OL,9,Fdriving.
OL,11,FThousands of road users have uploaded
OL,12,Ffootage to a portal which allows
OL,13,Fpolice to use the images as evidence -
OL,14,Fbut it's brought concern about what
OL,15,Fhas been called "DIY road cops".
OL,17,FAround seven million vehicles now have
OL,18,Fdashcams, and our new data shows it's
OL,19,Fchanging how our roads are policed.
