OL,7,FNew figures given to ITV News show
OL,8,F146,560 uploads to the National
OL,9,FDashcam Safety Portal, which allows
OL,10,Fpolice to use footage as evidence. So
OL,11,Ffar this year there have been 43,450
OL,12,Fclips sent to the system.
OL,14,FThe dashcam portal also accepts mobile
OL,15,Fphone footage or clips from any
OL,16,Frecording device, but some people have
OL,17,Fquestioned whether this should all be
OL,18,Fleft to the professionals.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
