OL,7,FWe spoke to PC Darren Ferneyhough of
OL,8,Fthe West Midlands Police, he said: "We
OL,9,Faren't asking people to go out there
OL,10,Fand film on purpose, it is more ad-hoc
OL,11,Fand if they catch an offence on a
OL,12,Fdashcam and it is serious enough, we
OL,13,Fwill prosecute and take positive
OL,14,Faction."
OL,16,FBy uploading video clips of dangerous
OL,17,Fdrivers, organisers of the dashcam
OL,18,Fportal estimate that the equivalent of
OL,19,Fmore than a century of police time has
OL,20,Fbeen saved.
