OL,7,FBut with so much footage now being
OL,8,Fuploaded, is there a risk of swamping
OL,9,Fpolice? Bryn Brooker is a dashcam
OL,10,Fexpert from the Nextbase tech company.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FHe said: "The great thing about the
OL,18,FNational Dashcam Safety Portal is it
OL,19,Fis helping police process evidence
OL,20,Ffaster. They can process ten pieces of
OL,21,Fevidence in less than 30 minutes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
