OL,7,F"At the moment, around 70% of all
OL,8,Fuploads are actioned. So that action
OL,9,Fcan range from anywhere up to a
OL,10,Fwarning letter, right the way through
OL,11,Fto prosecution in court."
OL,13,FTo upload video, road users can search
OL,14,Fonline for the National Dashcam Safety
OL,15,FPortal. Scotland isn't yet part of the
OL,16,Fsystem but there are plans to change
OL,17,Fthat, as millions of dashcams give
OL,18,Fpolice an unprecedented view of what's
OL,19,Fgoing wrong on our roads.
